{"tid":534841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個AIA嘉年華最惡頂同事","createTime":"2018-01-20T08:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T12:44:31.000Z","uid":54417,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5546750ecad9258a7a1c03ee63cb606a91b758","tid":534841,"uid":54417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 最惡頂真係非佢莫屬<br />\n<br />\n番左幾日 以為個滑梯大家姐已經夠on9 <br />\n點知過山車條TB仲撚惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過山車咁辛苦嘅位有放個女stuff<br />\n<br />\n死tb全日淨係坐係到撳手機同撳個開車制 <br />\n「入客收錢 幫手關閘 最辛苦開bar落客」依啲全撚部唔會做<br />\n就算另一個去頂食飯 得我同tb 佢都係咁坐係到玩手機同撳個一個制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOn9個客入黎佢遞錢比佢 都係坐係到玩手機無視<br />\n結果要啲客到後面比我<br />\n<br />\n佢成日去廁所 仲要次次都去成半個鐘 佢已經冇野做架啦<br />\n仲可以咁厚面皮去咁撚耐"},{"pid":"73c86eff725b0b2b5296484ac6ac7012adbb1269","tid":534841,"uid":83594,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"咁你有無罵佢？"},{"pid":"fdf13ec22a846ecd6505ebef38ffe2cd4ed5632b","tid":534841,"uid":69421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"返乜撚野呀 qui啦垃圾aia"},{"pid":"5fe34bc2b26006a536d457cd806e72d324639b2f","tid":534841,"uid":69421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdf13ec22a846ecd6505ebef38ffe2cd4ed5632b","tid":534841,"uid":69421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"返乜撚野呀 qui啦垃圾aia"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"Quit"},{"pid":"38c926c1a10870733a36ae111f0d3d4d7d3360a7","tid":534841,"uid":50663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"咁同自爆有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\